headline: The New York Stock Exchange Appoints Bryan Daniel to Lead NYSE Texas and Announces Location of NYSE Texas Headquarters
summary: NEW YORK, August 04, 2025--The New York Stock Exchange, part of Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced the appointment of Bryan Daniel as President, NYSE Texas and establishment of the headquarters of NYSE Texas. In this role, Bryan will report directly to Lynn Martin, President, NYSE Group.
